RoundcubePlugins - ChangeLog
============================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 2.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: Routine for installation of the sabre/vobject composer package that is required by the libcalendaring library
    Fixed: Couldn't create recurring events due to incompatible libcalendaring library version (calendar plugin)
    Fixed: Installation failure on SGBD with SQL strict mode enabled (SQL migration files)
    Fixed: Wrong password scheme in use with i-MSCP Serie 1.4.x. In i-MSCP Serie 1.4.x passwords are hashed (password plugin)
    Removed: Unmaintained pop3fetcher plugin - Will be re-integrated only if someone is taking care of it
    Removed: Unmaintained dkimstatus plugin - Will be re-integrated only if someone is taking care of it
    Updated: calendar plugin to version 3.2.8
    Updated: contextmenu plugin to version 2.1.2
    Updated: lilbcalendaring library to version 3.2.8
    Updated: odvviewer plugin to version 3.2.3
    Updated: pdfviewer plugin to version 3.2.5
    Updated: rcguard plugin to version 1.0.7
    Updated: tasklist plugin to version 3.2.8

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Dovecot (2.x) `autocreate' plugin is now enabled by i-MSCP Core (API 1.0.6)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Updated: Roundcube plugin pop3fetcher

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: Password config options
    Added: Managesieve vacation responses (out-of-office)
    Added: Roundcube reCAPTCHA plugin (rcguard 1.0.5)
    Added: Roundcube plugin vcard_attachments
    Changed: Default values for archive and managesieve
    Changed: Managesieve requirements check
    Changed: Run cronjob with lower priority
    Changed: Switch from imscp_pw_changer to password plugin
    Changed: The Managesieve plugin is now disabled by default to make package installation optional
    Fixed: Check that Roundcube is installed
    Fixed: Could not update from version 1.1.0 due to duplicate columns
    Fixed: Deletion of Roundcube plugins on uninstall
    Fixed: Regex for archive and managesieve plugins
    Removed: Experimental smartmatch operator
    Removed: Roundcube plugin imscp_pw_changer
    Updated: additional_message_headers config file
    Updated: Roundcube plugin calendar
    Updated: Roundcube plugin contextmenu
    Updated: Roundcube plugin logon_page
    Updated: Roundcube plugin odfviewer
    Updated: Roundcube plugin pdfviewer
    Updated: Roundcube plugin tasklist

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Database username is not escaped in password changer configuration file
    Fixed: Do not restart imscp_panel service when running in setup mode
    Fixed: Missing database port in password changer configuration file
    Fixed: Wrong check for managesieve plugin tasks
    Fixed #IP-1390: Password is not escaped in roundcube plugins imscp_password_changer conffile

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: imscp_panel service must be restarted to force flush of any opcode cache

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Roundcube version is badly checked resulting to installation failure

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Roundcube version check
    Removed: Support for i-MSCP 1.1.x serie

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: odfviewer
    Updated: calendar
    Updated: contextmenu
    Updated: dkimstatus
    Updated: libcalendaring
    Updated: pdfviewer

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Read/Update permissions on the mail_users ( i-MSCP database ) are now set by the package installer
    Updated: License headers for new year

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Plugin is not compatible with Roundcube 1.x serie
    Fixed: Read/Update permissions on the mail_users ( i-MSCP database ) are now set by the package installer
    Fixed: PO server implementation in use must be checked ( Some plugins don't work with Dovecot )
    Removed: send_request() from imscp_pw_changer ( sql.php )

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.9
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: my variable $rs masks earlier declaration

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.8
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: i-MSCP password changer
    Fixed: Roundcube plugins wont be activated after installation
    Changed: Plugin now use the database migration API provided by i-MSCP

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.7
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Backend file path in cronjob

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Missing array on listener

